{"tid":1613804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新活動][拋磚]和你lunch 上線囉~","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T00:37:14.000Z","uid":53590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5027faff72e2c5081445090a4e778816575a1595","tid":1613804,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:37:17.000Z","msg":"各位打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴絲<br />\n射太多波驚比老細屌罷唔到工？<br />\n見到啲學生日日走出嚟想幫手？<br />\n聽日開始<br />\n一齊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你lunch</span></span>啦<br />\n<br />\n作為一隻同大家一樣嘅打工奴材<br />\n眼見今日中環咁成功<br />\n但又唔喺附近返工參加唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如就整個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">量產型嘅翻版10.2中環西裝集會啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n遍地7區嘅好處係咩？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家就腳 易聚 易散 防不勝防</span><br />\n既然返工放lunch都係幾條毒撚上連登食飯盒<br />\n不如同其他公司嘅OL 靚仔 出嚟散步啦！<br />\n坐咗成日 散步身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功嘅話仲可以keep住做<br />\n反正大家<span style=\"color: gold;\">咁愛返工 日日都要食飯啦</span><br />\n<br />\n知到未必個個都中環返工<br />\n咁就不如好似10.1咁分6 7區<br />\n北角鰂魚涌嘅加入銅鑼灣<br />\n牛頭角九龍灣觀塘嘅加入黃大仙<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點分區就交比各區巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小小idea"},{"pid":"f807c761d23cc7f444b129f8dc5d518da6f01481","tid":1613804,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"淨係鰂魚涌都有好多office"},{"pid":"dc011321c1bdfb6bf33e40cc000283f42f9bb3f5","tid":1613804,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"自推 <br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"04554f07eaa82f0520f076f16704a5bbf78eba74","tid":1613804,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"cd6651b9fd36ff1e2fc18ded95523da82a6a2f72","tid":1613804,"